#############################
### SimLongi package news ###
#############################

Please report weird or unexpected behavior to Philip Pallmann <pallmann@biostat.uni-hannover.de>

#########################

Version 1.3 (7 October 2014)

- Added a function for calculating the approximate power (any-pair, all-pairs, global) of MCTs.

#########################

Version 1.2 (2 June 2014)

- Added functions for computing effective sample sizes for arbitrary gls and lme models.

#########################

Version 1.1-5 (7 May 2014)

- Bug fix: SimLongi() and SimLongiMMM() no longer surrender when data have missing values.

#########################

Version 1.1-4 (30 April 2014)

- Additional background aesthetics for PlotCI().

#########################

Version 1.1-3 (17 April 2014)

- Bug fix: comparisons of time points per treatment are now correctly labelled. 

#########################

Version 1.1-2 (4 April 2014)

- Help pages revised and updated.

#########################

Version 1.1-1 (1 April 2014)

- Added (a skeleton of) a pdf vignette.

#########################

Version 1.1 (31 March 2014)

- New functions for convenient selection among various mixed-effects models and subsequent multiple inference.

#########################

Version 1.0 (23 January 2014)

- Some basic functionality.